# 2026-05-22: api/ folder mostly excluded from Vercel deploys.
#
# Why: Vercel deploys were failing at "Provisioning Integrations" because
# the tradewithvarsha-db Turso integration couldn't provision a DB branch
# (likely the TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN got rotated and the integration's stored
# credential went stale). By excluding the api/ endpoints that import
# @libsql/client (auth, admin, bootstrap-admin, diag, _lib) the Turso
# integration stops being invoked and deploys succeed.
#
# 2026-07-19: un-ignored two leaf functions that DO NOT touch Turso —
# api/chat.js (Gemini proxy, pure fetch) and api/scan/on-demand.js
# (Yahoo/Stooq scanner, pure fetch). These are safe to deploy because
# they don't trigger the Turso integration. Everything else in api/
# stays excluded.

# Ignore the specific api endpoints + libs that use @libsql/client
api/_lib/
api/admin/
api/auth/
api/bootstrap-admin.ts
api/diag.ts
api/node_modules/
api/package.json
api/package-lock.json

server/
.claude/
*.log
